{"tid":1380302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（緊急）想8月5罷工成功，即刻去政府合署做文宣+連儂化","createTime":"2019-07-29T03:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T17:00:11.000Z","uid":86741,"like":76,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"030f5492eceb8a447c2fb53a33855866b9d9fbae","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:41:35.000Z","msg":"（少少長文，希望大家花少少時間睇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n想講<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">8月5日罷工</span></span>成功與否對呢個運動來講好關鍵，而成功與否又好視乎公務員嘅取態。目前已經有公務員發起<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">8月2日集會</span></span>，暫時未知會有幾多人，最理想係8月2當日凝聚到共識一齊8月5罷工。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GxzWMqn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGxzWMqn.png&h=3aa50623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公務員分析</span><br />\n<br />\n問題係，公務員都有好多種。目前大部分公務員都係持觀望態度。雖然遮名貼證出聲明係好鼓舞，但因為呢件事成本較低，一去到罷工即係暴露身份，難免會有猶豫，怕比office的藍絲批鬥/秋後算帳。分析下唔同公務員嘅想法：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1）舊制公務員：</strong>呢班人退休後有長糧，福利極多（房屋、醫療、子女教育津貼等）。且大部分年紀較大（當佢最遲2000年18歲入職 最後生都37），更甚有啲就嚟退休，對佢地嚟講社會愈穩定愈好，所以<span style=\"color: red;\">唔會介意要加入維穩一方。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2）高級公務員（pt.34或以上）/首長級人員</strong>：除左部分專業職系/AO/紀律部隊，大部分升得高級公務員/首長級人員嘅喺政府都做左超過19年，即係舊制嘅point對佢地apply。而愈接近權力核心，佢地知得愈多，好多時要同部門立場一致，更加<span style=\"color: red;\">唔敢有個人立場</span>。肯升上pt.34嘅人都有一定野心，重視前途及發展，更加怕秋後算帳。呢班人參與<span style=\"color: red;\">罷工嘅成本極大</span>，但偏偏效果最好，因為<span style=\"color: gold;\">每個人嘅崗位都係舉足輕重，絕對能癱瘓政府。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>3）新制公務員</strong>：呢班人2000年後入職，除左ACO或以下職系仲有得排公屋，基本上只係得返個爛鬼現金津貼。亦要參與強姦金，有長糧，福利與舊制相比已大不如前。由於佢地相對較後生，可塑性高，最壞打算都可以東家唔打打西家，<span style=\"color: gold;\">罷工成本相對較低</span>。佢地多數係前線公務員。呢班人正正係最能夠support罷工/抗爭活動，據我觀察大部分貼證出嚟嘅人都係屬於呢班人。<br />\n<br />\n上述分析只係in general去睇，不排除有良心舊制/高級公務員（首長級真係唔覺）。亦有部分新制係唔出聲等風向。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UHbumZ1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUHbumZ1.png&h=ad1b401d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">策略分析</span><br />\n<br />\n由於已經有人發起2/8公務員集會+5/8全港罷工，我地要諗下點先可以maximize 到兩日都join嘅人數，有見罷工同日有七區集會，我建議由<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">今晚開始集中喺呢七區嘅政府合署做文宣+起連儂牆，由門口、地下大堂、𨋢口直至每一層樓嘅office都要貼爆佢。</span></span>政府合署係開放比所有市民，尤其係啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">開放比市民交申請/參加活動嘅部門辦事處（e.g 康文、運輸、社署）</span>更加要貼爆佢。要喺呢個星期內令返工嘅公務員都睇到文宣，潛移默化佢地一定要出席2/8嘅集會，先有機會搞得成5/8嘅罷工。<br />\n<br />\n行動時間：<br />\n政府合署內：建議每晚8-10pm<br />\n政府合署門口：10pm後<br />\n原因係可以make sure 班公務員第2朝返工一定睇到，佢working hour 清我地夜晚再貼，亦避免同藍絲公務員正面衝突，強調撕一貼十。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人數：3-5人成團<br />\n<br />\n貼嘅內容：<br />\n主力貼<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">2/8集會</span>同<span style=\"color: purple;\">5/8罷工</span></span>文宣，建議要吸納公務員入面嘅游離分子。貼<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑警濫暴</span>。好多中立/藍絲公務員淨係睇港人港地呢啲維穩page，根本冇睇過其他媒體。動之以情：<span style=\"color: gold;\">拉攏有子女嘅舊制公務員，</span>你安穩姐，你想唔想你兩腳一伸之後仔女面對地獄般嘅生活？貼<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新疆慘況</span>逼佢地面對。<br />\n<br />\n以下係七區政府合署地址（from google)：<br />\n<br />\n屯門政府合署：屯喜路1號屯門政府合署<br />\n<br />\n荃灣政府合署：荃灣西樓角路38號<br />\n<br />\n大埔政府合署：新界大埔汀角路1號<br />\n<br />\n沙田政府合署：香港新界沙田上禾輋路1號<br />\n<br />\n旺角政府合署：香港九龍旺角聯運街30號<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙民政諮詢中心：九龍黃大仙龍翔道 138 號龍翔辦公大樓 2 樓 201室<br />\n<br />\n金鐘（直接貼政總）：香港島金鐘添馬添美道2號<br />\n<br />\n希望大家理解好多公務員唔肯行多一步都係受朋輩/老闆壓力，如果可以凝造到一個氣氛，知道有幾多同路人，佢地都會夠膽企出嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e14c83cc8b5eb0ea0d0bd8dfdff830cd9d3fc3","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:45:33.000Z","msg":"自己推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64123be8da644981ecc9d736a3c8c8481e85418","tid":1380302,"uid":265256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:46:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bd2b0f51108c6f9db82bd2f506b88083e90ad3da","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:51:17.000Z","msg":"自己推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07192cb61052a5a436153b294a70d32a494c8ef2","tid":1380302,"uid":288602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:53:40.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"550d555fe1f52a9e7ee6a75c71c2a9bdeb0c6c91","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:07:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8375d8311c017cb7d472301b480762e9872b1f92","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:11:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"164d34e5e0c957bc8b9d69b0b69e690550c75caf","tid":1380302,"uid":282718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:16:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14e1da37010d3aeee5a94d65eca2799a27af6cf9","tid":1380302,"uid":182802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:17:15.000Z","msg":"推 一定要比公務員睇到"},{"pid":"5e4967fe922a20569368b6b75ba15c690ea705c8","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:18:43.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8895fbb8cef45eaccb556590d4d131b00b8e0b97","tid":1380302,"uid":276948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:26:53.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"efa5591276f1a86a06b03cc12ea70df1fc88cb3e","tid":1380302,"uid":17133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:27:26.000Z","msg":"8月5號大罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e99e9e84b89eb7d8240aaf570dabbc2f057535","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:32:48.000Z","msg":"怒推"},{"pid":"97a7885252dabbac7585cebfbc7d16d0aeab6a96","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:51:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b43042cd0a811134d66e2c3524d599fbefd0f45","tid":1380302,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:51:57.000Z","msg":"[公務員]今日腦細傾緊點樣返工<br />\n租車/的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點都要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9238281e207adb0d03defdad574aad34489807ca","tid":1380302,"uid":234242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:57:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"95ffe2ffa15abd13c784fd40efe0591d40fcb7f7","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8b43042cd0a811134d66e2c3524d599fbefd0f45","tid":1380302,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:51:57.000Z","msg":"[公務員]今日腦細傾緊點樣返工<br />\n租車/的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點都要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:58:38.000Z","msg":"啲高層真係唔識架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14479ded304066a57f619143ea40ab16854bdbd4","tid":1380302,"uid":268656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:16:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34e7b802bb2024e63cfb94d43aa14c70135c2a1a","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:24:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"705262020101f28cbb69cb62de007e61c7f5d57b","tid":1380302,"uid":161848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:28:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"37d7ec3c76c4d30ec4b2872a49dcda8d20a9f703","tid":1380302,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:58:27.000Z","msg":"罷工"},{"pid":"f07bc2f5c155d8ed05371949ec163b0510835b14","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:05:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"10827e4fda2040d5c6db24903964dded3b5e9be0","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:24:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d0ee2f6f3b9836710cde91af86fe56d2c452419d","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:41:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9fc586ffa3b432cc048319c7df984bad964a92fa","tid":1380302,"uid":26820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/38V69LU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F38V69LU.png&h=00f1391b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPish"},{"pid":"11e1a0c2bf544d3c00d6d198d4d02bdf153e2dfe","tid":1380302,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:43:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推! 8月5罷工!!!!! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月29)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"53717447ddde28b9fcbd046740534e356b5ca620","tid":1380302,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42daf8359a75d9dbedda60b7f54a3bd8d7745339","tid":1380302,"uid":188482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b43042cd0a811134d66e2c3524d599fbefd0f45","tid":1380302,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:51:57.000Z","msg":"[公務員]今日腦細傾緊點樣返工<br />\n租車/的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點都要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:50:30.000Z","msg":"做公務員做得咁認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43fcaeb458f660b6099a00ceb5056336fe829373","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T06:52:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"90e6614b6335dd35332d5ff34858a12bd01b685b","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:17:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5e08200fc917b1af8129516397e717e10c270b15","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:08:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a90c483d7bd4daafa285e47baff2470671a21013","tid":1380302,"uid":268656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:47:11.000Z","msg":"85"},{"pid":"103c0369fc970c1064e0ca40f376180db4c04bd7","tid":1380302,"uid":79165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"030f5492eceb8a447c2fb53a33855866b9d9fbae","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:41:35.000Z","msg":"（少少長文，希望大家花少少時間睇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n想講<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">8月5日罷工</span></span>成功與否對呢個運動來講好關鍵，而成功與否又好視乎公務員嘅取態。目前已經有公務員發起<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">8月2日集會</span></span>，暫時未知會有幾多人，最理想係8月2當日凝聚到共識一齊8月5罷工。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GxzWMqn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGxzWMqn.png&h=3aa50623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公務員分析</span><br />\n<br />\n問題係，公務員都有好多種。目前大部分公務員都係持觀望態度。雖然遮名貼證出聲明係好鼓舞，但因為呢件事成本較低，一去到罷工即係暴露身份，難免會有猶豫，怕比office的藍絲批鬥/秋後算帳。分析下唔同公務員嘅想法：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1）舊制公務員：</strong>呢班人退休後有長糧，福利極多（房屋、醫療、子女教育津貼等）。且大部分年紀較大（當佢最遲2000年18歲入職 最後生都37），更甚有啲就嚟退休，對佢地嚟講社會愈穩定愈好，所以<span style=\"color: red;\">唔會介意要加入維穩一方。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2）高級公務員（pt.34或以上）/首長級人員</strong>：除左部分專業職系/AO/紀律部隊，大部分升得高級公務員/首長級人員嘅喺政府都做左超過19年，即係舊制嘅point對佢地apply。而愈接近權力核心，佢地知得愈多，好多時要同部門立場一致，更加<span style=\"color: red;\">唔敢有個人立場</span>。肯升上pt.34嘅人都有一定野心，重視前途及發展，更加怕秋後算帳。呢班人參與<span style=\"color: red;\">罷工嘅成本極大</span>，但偏偏效果最好，因為<span style=\"color: gold;\">每個人嘅崗位都係舉足輕重，絕對能癱瘓政府。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>3）新制公務員</strong>：呢班人2000年後入職，除左ACO或以下職系仲有得排公屋，基本上只係得返個爛鬼現金津貼。亦要參與強姦金，有長糧，福利與舊制相比已大不如前。由於佢地相對較後生，可塑性高，最壞打算都可以東家唔打打西家，<span style=\"color: gold;\">罷工成本相對較低</span>。佢地多數係前線公務員。呢班人正正係最能夠support罷工/抗爭活動，據我觀察大部分貼證出嚟嘅人都係屬於呢班人。<br />\n<br />\n上述分析只係in general去睇，不排除有良心舊制/高級公務員（首長級真係唔覺）。亦有部分新制係唔出聲等風向。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UHbumZ1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUHbumZ1.png&h=ad1b401d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">策略分析</span><br />\n<br />\n由於已經有人發起2/8公務員集會+5/8全港罷工，我地要諗下點先可以maximize 到兩日都join嘅人數，有見罷工同日有七區集會，我建議由<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">今晚開始集中喺呢七區嘅政府合署做文宣+起連儂牆，由門口、地下大堂、𨋢口直至每一層樓嘅office都要貼爆佢。</span></span>政府合署係開放比所有市民，尤其係啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">開放比市民交申請/參加活動嘅部門辦事處（e.g 康文、運輸、社署）</span>更加要貼爆佢。要喺呢個星期內令返工嘅公務員都睇到文宣，潛移默化佢地一定要出席2/8嘅集會，先有機會搞得成5/8嘅罷工。<br />\n<br />\n行動時間：<br />\n政府合署內：建議每晚8-10pm<br />\n政府合署門口：10pm後<br />\n原因係可以make sure 班公務員第2朝返工一定睇到，佢working hour 清我地夜晚再貼，亦避免同藍絲公務員正面衝突，強調撕一貼十。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人數：3-5人成團<br />\n<br />\n貼嘅內容：<br />\n主力貼<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">2/8集會</span>同<span style=\"color: purple;\">5/8罷工</span></span>文宣，建議要吸納公務員入面嘅游離分子。貼<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑警濫暴</span>。好多中立/藍絲公務員淨係睇港人港地呢啲維穩page，根本冇睇過其他媒體。動之以情：<span style=\"color: gold;\">拉攏有子女嘅舊制公務員，</span>你安穩姐，你想唔想你兩腳一伸之後仔女面對地獄般嘅生活？貼<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新疆慘況</span>逼佢地面對。<br />\n<br />\n以下係七區政府合署地址（from google)：<br />\n<br />\n屯門政府合署：屯喜路1號屯門政府合署<br />\n<br />\n荃灣政府合署：荃灣西樓角路38號<br />\n<br />\n大埔政府合署：新界大埔汀角路1號<br />\n<br />\n沙田政府合署：香港新界沙田上禾輋路1號<br />\n<br />\n旺角政府合署：香港九龍旺角聯運街30號<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙民政諮詢中心：九龍黃大仙龍翔道 138 號龍翔辦公大樓 2 樓 201室<br />\n<br />\n金鐘（直接貼政總）：香港島金鐘添馬添美道2號<br />\n<br />\n希望大家理解好多公務員唔肯行多一步都係受朋輩/老闆壓力，如果可以凝造到一個氣氛，知道有幾多同路人，佢地都會夠膽企出嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:49:35.000Z","msg":"印埋d罪證<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/2390192077739953/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F200976479994868%2Fposts%2F2390192077739953%2F&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67TcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=43eed6f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/200976479994868/posts/2390192077739953/</a>"},{"pid":"92b577eef68a8c5b1f01ac2e68dab36d38e39c66","tid":1380302,"uid":70443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:05:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4452d934adfd670bfb72dc288acbc89c8bacc525","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92b577eef68a8c5b1f01ac2e68dab36d38e39c66","tid":1380302,"uid":70443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:05:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903f1d0e6122ee100b8116119bf2cf87a34a15a1","tid":1380302,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ac41570c39b66ab858c08ca5f7ea0f2ddd6ad3a","tid":1380302,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:35:16.000Z","msg":"公墓員罷工會有好強既號召力！"},{"pid":"3b491cef801556cedf6ffe03891e120bb99359a6","tid":1380302,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:35:28.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"53bd5f212cffce762119dda0bbb09fcec35d6be2","tid":1380302,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:36:31.000Z","msg":"不要只 「推/push」 comment下做宣傳 好似我咁<br />\n<br />\n我地連罷工、老豆接仔放工都未試<br />\n香港人 唔好放棄!<br />\n__________________<br />\n<br />\n*7月30 : 地鐵不合作運動 <br />\n*8月2 : 公務員罷工集會<br />\n*8月5 : 一齊罷工 7區集會 <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">返工放工幫手air drop</span><br />\n停止前線義士受傷被捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我要真普選 不要空降假特首</span>"},{"pid":"23b152f174f5264a079ceee893120b2635886320","tid":1380302,"uid":70443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:14:22.000Z","msg":"Push ar dllm"},{"pid":"a2459c7fd2cac2d21afb517cd559e5c9338935c1","tid":1380302,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:15:48.000Z","msg":"730大塞車85大罷工"},{"pid":"800e4c4ba60f2ac49d3a4436b0156e0afa8e77b3","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:18:27.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7f4b3b18a7967770364262d9b1fa931f84b3b12f","tid":1380302,"uid":70443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:28:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d6bede1ebde9cbd7c71ad134af7f47732c4146ac","tid":1380302,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:31:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5858824ea0ab17482c9afb88c0d48eb78fe7120f","tid":1380302,"uid":86741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT